message:
Continuing to learn new information is important when working in the anti-human trafficking field. 
“Sergeant Blalock says she came away better prepared, and even a veteran officer can tune up what they do on the job.”

data.description: “How long does it take for the pimps to build that relationship with the victims before they actually make their move and bring them into sex trafficking?”
data.title: Selling Kids: Facing your trafficker in court
